Evangel University Logo Evangel University is a private Christian university with an embedded seminary in Springfield, Missouri, United States. It is affiliated with the Assemblies of God Christian denomination, which is also headquartered in Springfield. The former Evangel College was renamed Evangel University on June 8, 1998. The campus sits on 80 acres that were originally part of O’Reilly General Hospital. Source
